      "instruction": "<p>Combine 1/2 tbsp per person of your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(save the rest for later!) in a bowl with your<strong> ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>paprika</strong>, <strong>garam masala </strong>and <strong>ginger paste</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a squeeze of<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon</strong> <strong>juice </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>tikka</strong> <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
