    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>diced</strong> <strong>chicken breast </strong>to the tikka<strong> </strong>marinade<strong> </strong>and give everything a good mix up until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1602247841821-x200.jpg",
