          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> to the pan and cook for 12-15 min, stirring occasionally until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken tikka</strong></p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p><p>Add your <strong>naan[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
