    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warmed naan</strong> topped with the <strong>chicken tikka </strong>and <strong>Indian-style salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>mint yoghurt </strong>and garnish<strong> </strong>with a<strong> remaining lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
